  "description": "<i>Robin Hood</i> is a action game in the style of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=The+Legend+of+Zelda\">The Legend of Zelda</a>. You control Robin Hood from a top-down perspective. You'll have to explore, fight enemies, solve puzzles and acquire items to progress in the game. You can shoot enemies with arrows or hit them with a staff or sword. The game's targeting system allows the player to lock onto a target while walking in other directions. Acquired items can be bought and sold and NPC characters can be spoken with for hints and plot progression. The game features fifteen levels.",
